            <span class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-3">2</span>
            Data-Driven Analysis
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <p>
              Using your actual profit & loss statement and sales data, I calculate exactly how much money 
              each technology improvement will save or earn you. No vague promises—real numbers based on your specific restaurant.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">You'll receive:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">→</span>
                A complete review of what systems you have and which ones overlap
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">→</span>
                Projected savings and revenue for each recommended change
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">→</span>
                A step-by-step plan with clear goals and timelines
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">→</span>
                Full cost breakdown and payment options
              </li>
